            Return resolveMethods(trim(concat(concat(concat(recvPrefix(concat(bef, "")), " "), mapSet(recv, jsEvalIn(trim(item 1 of args), env), jsEvalIn(trim(item 2 of args), env))), methodRest(aft))), env).
    If substringBefore(expr, " . get (") is not equal to expr:
